Hong Kong Stocks Close 3 Percent Lower
HONG KONG , November 30 ( Xinhua ) -- Hong Kong stocks lost 339.79 points , or 3.16 percent , to finish at 10,402.32 Monday .
Market turnover amounted to 5.085 billion HK dollars ( 652 million U.S. dollars ) , 709 million HK dollars ( 91 million U.S. dollars ) less than that of Friday .
The key Hang Seng Index fell 36.92 points , or 0.34 percent , to open at 10,705.19 Monday morning , and then lost 232.30 points , or 2.16 percent , to close the morning session at 10 , 509.81 .
The HSI fell 36.81 points , or 0.34 percent , to close trading at 10,742.11 last Friday .
